Laurent Blanc vacates his job as manager of the France national football team following his team's exit from the tournament. (BBC) (ESPN)Ernesto Valverde is appointed Valencia CF coach until the end of the season, replacing Mauricio Pellegrino, who was sacked two days ago. (ESPN)Harry Redknapp is appointed as the manager of Queens Park Rangers, taking over from Mark Hughes whose contract was terminated after fail to win any of their 12 Premier League games this season. (The Independent) (The Guardian)